ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>
[The authorities were prudent to act so swiftly. There are other diseases
-- such as vesicular stomatitis -- that produce lesions similar to those
caused by FMD and testing is required to make the distinction. We await
official confirmation of the eventual test results. - Mod.TG]
